title: The Tudors - Season 4 - Opening Intro
author: GotPilot
comment: I love the fact that in the end of the theme they put little and fast images of the characters that are dead! It feels like they are still part of it all, like if Henry is still haunted by them!
Sarah Bolger is so gorgeous as Mary wow
I'm thankful that I love History!
Omg Tamzin Merchant is so pretty, I love her! 😍😍
Beautiful show, especially the last episode!
